dc_title_s: Carte du front français d'après la carte d'Europe publiée par la Société d'Editions géographiques, maritimes et coloniales
dc_description_s: Covers eastern part of France to western border Czechoslovakia, Copenhagen in north to Florence in south.; Shows cities, towns, roads, waterways, and the location of troops and fortifications along the French front.; Relief shown by shading and spot heights.; Depths shown by isolines.|72 x 52 Centimeters|Scale approximately 1:1,960,784|General Map Collection
